properties.headline: ALPINE CONDITIONS - PERISHER AND BEYOND Kosciuszko Road
properties.otherAdvice:
Road open to Perisher.
Beyond Perisher: Road closed.

Throughout the winter period:

- Kosciuszko Rd is closed between Perisher and Charlotte Pass.
- Link Rd is closed between Smiggin Holes and Guthega Road.

Chains must be carried in Kosciuszko National Park in winter (4WDs exempt). All motorists should be prepared and equipped for sudden changes in road and weather conditions in Alpine areas.
